git gui difftool is a script using in git-gui,make it easy to use visual diff tool in git-gui.

setting:
-modify the DIFFTOOL in git_gui_difftool.py to the visual diff tool command you are using
-git gui
-menu->Tools
-fill in Add Tool dialog:
 -Name: for example "difftool"
 -Command: "YOUR_PATH_TO_git_gui_difftool.py $FILENAME"
 -Don't show the command output window:☑
 -Run only if a diff is selected ($FILENAME not empty):☑
 -Add globally:☑

usage:
-git gui
-click at the file you want to visual diff
-menu->Tools->the menu you just setting
